<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2020</DATELINE><TITLE>Study on the effect of nursing-technology integrated in the imaging examination of Novel coronavirus pneumonia</TITLE><BODY>Currently, the outbreak of the new coronary pneumonia has entered a critical period of screening, prevention and control.In order to block the transmission of the virus in the radiology department, it is particularly important to effectively protect the medical servant while speeding up the flow of inspection.Based on the basis of notification of the bureau of disease control and prevention, the expert consensus of the CMA and CMDA, and the literature review, combined with the previous practical work experience,this article puts forward the recommendations on the important effect of nursing-technology integrated in the imaging examination of novel coronavirus pneumonia, in order to provide reference for the protection of medical servant in the radiology department at the front line of anti-epidemic.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>